import React from 'react';
import {
  LineStage, 
  Steps, 
  Step, 
  Phase, 
  PhaseTitle, 
  ContainerSteps,
  Container
} from './styles';

function StageComponent() { 
  return (
    <>
      <Container>
        <LineStage />
        <ContainerSteps>
          <Steps>
            <Step>
              <Phase/>
              <PhaseTitle>Cart</PhaseTitle>
            </Step>
            <Step>
              <Phase/>
              <PhaseTitle>Payment options</PhaseTitle>
            </Step>
            <Step>
              <Phase/>
              <PhaseTitle>Receipt</PhaseTitle>
            </Step>
          </Steps>
        </ContainerSteps>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}
export default StageComponent;
